WEBVTT

00:01.457 --> 00:06.224
<i>[Sam Narrating] Leaping about in time,</i>
<i>I've found that there are some things</i>
<i>in life that I can't change,</i>

00:06.296 --> 00:09.197
<i>and there are some things</i>
<i>that I can.</i>

00:09.265 --> 00:12.564
<i>To save a life,</i>
<i>to change a heart,</i>

00:12.635 --> 00:14.568
<i>to make the right choice.</i>

00:14.637 --> 00:17.470
<i>I guess that's what life's about</i>...

00:17.540 --> 00:20.532
<i>making the right choice</i>
<i>at the right time.</i>

00:22.000 --> 00:28.074
